#

Chocolate Chip Waffles

25 min
$8.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastBrunchDessert

Description

Fluffy waffles loaded with sweet chocolate chips, perfect for breakfast or a delightful treat!

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 1 ½ cups
  • baking powder: 1 tablespoon
  • sugar: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: ½ teaspoon
  • milk: 1 cup
  • eggs: 2
  • vegetable oil: ¼ cup
  • chocolate chips: 1 cup
  • vanilla extract: 1 teaspoon
